GIT Prompt for BASH

    Picture worth a thousand words, see wiki for screenshots
    http://github.com/lvv/git-prompt/wikis


DEPENDENCY
	bash (tested with v3.2.33) 
	git  (optional)
	svn  (optional)
	sed
	tput (from terminfo)
	tty
	grep 
	locale
	id 


